{
  "title": "Grafana — внутренние метрики",
  "uid": "siem-grafana-metrics",
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "time": {
    "from": "now-24h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timezone": "browser",
  "tags": [
    "grafana",
    "monitoring",
    "siem"
  ],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "ℹ️ О дашборде Grafana",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 3
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Grafana Server — внутренние метрики\n\nМало «динамики» на графиках — **норма**, пока никто не кликает по UI. Ниже добавлены **HTTP** и **запросы datasource** — там больше линий при работе в Grafana.\n\nДубликат с англ. **Grafana metrics** в списке — обычно другой UID (импорт). Этот файл: **siem-grafana-metrics**.\n\n**SIEM-события:** дашборд **SIEM-Lite Overview**.\n\n**Настройка:** job `grafana` в `deploy/docker/prometheus.yml`\n\n---\n**Логи Docker:** внизу дашборда панель **«Loki: логи контейнеров SIEM»** (Promtail → Loki). Фильтр по `container` именам контейнеров."
      },
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "CPU (process)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-siem"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "rate(process_cpu_seconds_total{job=\"grafana\"}[2m]) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "CPU s/s"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "cps",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single"
        },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "hidden"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "RSS память",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-siem"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "process_resident_memory_bytes{job=\"grafana\"} or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "RSS"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "bytes",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single"
        },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "hidden"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Grafana UP",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 11,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-siem"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "up{job=\"grafana\"} or vector(0)",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "text": "DOWN",
                  "color": "red"
                },
                "1": {
                  "text": "UP",
                  "color": "green"
                }
              }
            }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Открытые файлы (process)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 11,
        "w": 18,
        "h": 4
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-siem"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "process_open_fds{job=\"grafana\"} or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "fds"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single"
        },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "hidden"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "HTTP Grafana / с (топ handler)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 15,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-siem"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "topk(10, sum by (handler) (rate(grafana_http_request_duration_seconds_count{job=\"grafana\"}[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{handler}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "cps",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 12
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "Запросы datasource / с (по type)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 15,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-siem"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (datasource_type) (rate(grafana_datasource_request_total{job=\"grafana\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{datasource_type}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "cps",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 12
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "title": "Loki: логи контейнеров SIEM",
      "description": "Стрим логов ключевых сервисов из Loki (docker_sd → label container).",
      "type": "logs",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 23,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 10
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki-siem"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki-siem"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "{container=~\"siem-clickhouse|siem-parser|siem-correlator|siem-vector-aggregator|siem-admin|siem-grafana|siem-prometheus|siem-redpanda\"}",
          "queryType": "range"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "dedupStrategy": "none",
        "enableLogDetails": true,
        "prettifyLogMessage": false,
        "showCommonLabels": false,
        "showLabels": true,
        "showTime": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending",
        "wrapLogMessage": true
      }
    }
  ]
}
